title: Iku Wholefood Kitchen - Rozelle
typeOfFood: Vegan, Japanese, Macrobiotic, Fast food, Take-out
description: Vegan chain macrobiotic ready made meals. Salads, rice balls, tofu fritters, casseroles, pies and tarts, lasagne, soup, curries, burgers, nori roll. Sweets include muffins, friands, slice, pies, sago pudding, black sticky rice. Organic drinks, bancha tea.
